{"tid":1529440,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵係敵人,但唔好無差別破壞","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T19:29:20.000Z","uid":298610,"like":17,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e76892f84a787711fda6b28b933801e2af8897c1","tid":1529440,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"各兄弟<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">無差別破壞只會令你印象扣分!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好浪費時間破壞售票機,控制室</span></span><br />\n控制室都有我地D兄弟,加上破壞<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇實際用途</span></span><br />\n比人感覺好差,包括我在內<br />\n新聞睇到都好核凸!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦比敵方拎黎做把柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日東涌站開消防喉都睇到我??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />??<br />\n<br />\n重點去返<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">破壞閘口同CCTV</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n給大家一個藉口免費搭鐵又唔敢衝即的朋友<br />\n利申:我一個人都好尷尬咁跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩同意的<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f469060e9ab642e75856486b82803c34feb7323","tid":1529440,"uid":130898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:37:31.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"045cece3bb75ad0a10dc8301ade3628cdbc7eaab","tid":1529440,"uid":122185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"和理非，好無力，好忟？<br />\n要抗爭，只有十月一前每日堅持做以下既事，係堅持，堅唔到都要堅，係呢到發誓你堅持呢個九月，就一個月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 罷消費（任何福建幫、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、藍紅食店）好難？勇武難唔難？<br />\n2. 低享樂（要發洩，做運動、十點9叫、唔好taobao消費食好野）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 每日like and share 1個文宣post<br />\n5. 下載Twitter 開acc,每日出1個post<br />\n6. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n7. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n8. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n9. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n10. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n11. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"ed4277559b5b10269d8337a210c4aa4b0689f5df","tid":1529440,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:41:42.000Z","msg":"閘口同CCTV"},{"pid":"e91e403faaa4ac214d9d209463c86206c5f5a9b8","tid":1529440,"uid":276715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"道德潔癖就死撚開啦"},{"pid":"66ea491e4f8f65ded769ee28380dbd366568afe8","tid":1529440,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e91e403faaa4ac214d9d209463c86206c5f5a9b8","tid":1529440,"uid":276715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"道德潔癖就死撚開啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"重點放係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">閘口同CCTV</span></span>,<br />\n唔好學黑警見人就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打得我早就直接打黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15db6dca740e79fbe345e56e133c291af21270f0","tid":1529440,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"pish!!"},{"pid":"59daca04bbb2beaa9aa96b4d9d41d74ca0ba0e97","tid":1529440,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:07:28.000Z","msg":"我知樓主講緊隻新game香城online裡面有新任務要打npc , 其實同火魔法同理，尻放無用兼樣衰，但阻止d怪行就好有用！"},{"pid":"077b7a9389227a60c674d634301190e0c3e17357","tid":1529440,"uid":269392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:08:12.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"c3e54c800bfdc694416e903cbbf4ba25166c2cad","tid":1529440,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59daca04bbb2beaa9aa96b4d9d41d74ca0ba0e97","tid":1529440,"ui